Hampton,Roads,Transit,is,a,regional,transportation,system,providing,bus,light,rail,and,ferry,services,for,Hampton,Roads,Virginia,The,Hampton,Roads,Transit,API,provides,programmatic,access,to,real,time,bus,data,Available,calls,include,bus,routes,current,bus,locations,and,more,The,API,is,able,to,return,data,on,the,entire,system,or,on,a,specified,route